                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/norway-offers-to-make-financial-resource.html?id=551755" title="">
                        Norway offers to make financial resources available to the IMF
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[28.03.2009]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Minister of Finance Kristin Halvorsen Friday sent a letter to the Managing Director of the International Monetary Fund (IMF) offering to make additional financial resources available to the Fund. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
