                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/regulations-relating-to-management-of-th.html?id=549847" title="">
                        Regulations relating to Management of the Government Bond Fund  
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.03.2009]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Finance laid down regulations relating to Folketrygdfondet’s management of the Government Bond Fund today. The Fund has been established with a ceiling of NOK 50 billion. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
