            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/siemens-under-observation-in-corruption-.html?id=549155" title="">
                        Siemens under observation in corruption case
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[13.03.2009]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Finance has decided to place the German company Siemens AG under observation due to the gross and systematic corruption the group has been involved in over many years. Gross corruption can be grounds for exclusion from the Government Pension Fund – Global. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
