            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/the-government-pension-fund---global-200.html?id=548597" title="">
                        The Government Pension Fund - Global: 2008 is the worst year in the history of the fund
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[11.03.2009]</p>
                <p>- The results of the Pension Fund – Global, which were presented by Norges Bank today, show that the Fund in 2008 was strongly influenced by the global financial crisis, says the Norwegian Minister of Finance, Ms Kristin Halvorsen.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
