            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/appointment-of-the-board-of-directors-of.html?id=548336" title="">
                        Appointment of the Board of Directors of the Norwegian State Finance Fund
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[06.03.2009]</p>
                <p>The King in Council has today appointed the Board of Directors for the Norwegian State Finance Fund. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <hr class="seperator" />   
    
