                <img src="/upload/FIN/Ingresssbilder/pressrelease.gif" alt="Press release" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/norway-presents-new-measures-for-industr.html?id=545244" title="">
                        Norway presents new measures for industry and households
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[08.02.2009]</p>
                <p>The Government proposes to establish two new funds with a total capital of NOK 100 billion. The funds will ease the access to loans for companies and households, and contribute to stabilise the financial market", says Norwegian Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
