                    <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/mining-company-excluded-from-the-governm.html?id=543107" title="">
                        Mining company excluded from the Government Pension Fund – Global due to contribution to serious environmental damage
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[30.01.2009]</p>
                <p>Based on a recommendation from the Council on Ethics for the Government Pension Fund – Global, the Ministry of Finance has excluded the Canadian mining company Barrick Gold Corporation from the Fund. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <hr class="seperator" />   
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/fin/press-center/Press-releases/2009/cluster-weapons-manufacturer-excluded-fr.html?id=543105" class="ISI_IGNORE">
